The script run_analysis.R performs the 5 steps described in the course project's definition.
Data is downloaded and unzipped in folder "./data". Then, read to data frames Activity_Train_data, Activity_Test_dataâ€¦ 
Train and test data are concatenated (merged vertically) using rbind in data frames named Activity_ data, Subject_data, and Features_data.
All data are joined (merged horizontally) using cbind in data frame named Data.
Data frame Data is the data frame used in ulterior tidying. See commentaries included in script run_analysis.R for further information.
